@startuml Activity_Earthquake_Monitoring
title Activity Diagram - Earthquake Monitoring

start
:Proxy /api/earthquakes fetches USGS feed
(bbox filtered to Turkey);
:Parse events into Earthquake entities;
:Render points on DeckGL/MapLibre layer;

repeat
  :User clicks earthquake marker;
  :Show popup (depth, magnitude, place, time);
repeat while (User explores more events?) is (yes)
->no;

if (Magnitude >= user threshold
AND matches MonitorPanel keyword?) then (yes)
  :Push notification to takiplistem panel;
else (no)
  :Keep event on map only;
endif

:User gains spatial/temporal awareness;
stop
@enduml
